      <hedline>
        <hl1>WASH YOUR HANDS</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>BBC reports that computer keyboards accumulate up to 2 grams of dirt every month, 56 percent of it coming from food (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Wonder where your keyboard has been? A BBC report says that computer keyboards accumulate up to 2 grams (about 0.07 ounces) of dirt every month. A study undertaken by AOL of Britain found that 56 percent of the nasty stuff came from food, but the study also found insects, dead skin and hair.</p>
      </block>
